          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "45f8d401-412a-43bb-9c70-457310bc1ba1",
              "name": "text",
              "value": "Date: 2 May 2026   Participants:   - Jagadeesh (Consultant)   - Adi (Client – Millet Powder Brand Owner)  ---  Adi: Currently I am running my millet powder business mainly through Instagram. Most of my orders come from DMs and WhatsApp messages.  Jagadeesh: Okay, so you don’t have a proper website or ordering system yet?  Adi: No, I don’t have any website. Everything is manual right now. I track orders in WhatsApp chats and sometimes in a notebook. It’s getting difficult to manage as orders are increasing.  Jagadeesh: Got it. That means you also don’t have a clear system to track total sales or customer data?  Adi: Yes, exactly. I don’t have proper tracking of daily or monthly sales. I also don’t have a customer database.  Jagadeesh: How are you handling customer support currently?  Adi: I reply manually on Instagram and WhatsApp. Sometimes I miss messages, especially when there are many inquiries.  Jagadeesh: Understood. What about your product certifications and licenses?  Adi: I have basic certifications, but they are not properly displayed anywhere online. Customers sometimes ask about authenticity.  Jagadeesh: That’s an important point. Having those visible builds trust.  Adi: Yes, I agree. I want to look more professional and scale the business.  Jagadeesh: Here’s what I suggest: 1. We create a proper website for your brand 2. Add an online ordering system 3. Track all orders and sales automatically 4. Set up a basic CRM for customer data 5. Display certifications clearly on the website 6. Improve customer support with a structured system  Adi: That sounds good. I really need all of that.  Jagadeesh: We can also integrate Instagram with your website so traffic converts better.  Adi: That would be very helpful.  Jagadeesh: I’ll help you set up everything step by step—from website to tracking and automation.  Adi: Perfect. Let’s proceed with that.  ---  Meeting End",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
